dct_title_s: Plan of Beach Haven Gardens on the Island of Long Beach, Ocean County N.J.
dct_description_sm: Sheet 1: Map covers area from 32nd Street to Maryland Avenue in Long Beach along the Atlantic Ocean. Map depicts the numbered property lots on each block in Long Beach and includes the property of Lemuel S. Gale.
Sheet 2: Map covers area from 23rd Street to Maryland Avenue along the Atlantic Ocean. Map depicts the properties of Spray Beach Hotel, Long Beach Railroad, and Lemuel S. Gale.
